Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:36.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:41.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:43.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:48.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:51.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:53.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:57.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.84,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:09.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:14.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:19.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:25.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:30.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:36.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:42.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:52.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:57.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:36.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛說愛「過於沉重」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:41.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轉變成恨之前　把它拒絕於心門之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:43.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬物皆是如此吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:48.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是把不合時宜的事隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:51.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是冒牌貨的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:53.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扭曲了的窘迫時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:57.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連本應定下約定的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.84,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會毫無察覺地擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:09.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始崩壞但曾經互相理解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其撇下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:14.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的末路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:19.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中不服　想與之對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:25.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要從當初墮落的印象中逃離開去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:30.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　就算歷經千百次也要找出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:36.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的雙眸　你手中的余溫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:42.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小聲嘟囔著「愛總是讓我遍體鱗傷…」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因畏懼堅信不疑的事而哭過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道軟弱才能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:52.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕堅信不疑地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:57.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是愛的真諦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎提斯坦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…阿扎提斯坦…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這規模  不是恐怖襲擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…那顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啦  正如你想的那樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:08.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#06 傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把傷員搬到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉換燈光角度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近找
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟…竟然做的這麼過分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把孩子們帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時把他們安置在避難所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強躲過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  基地卻變成這副慘像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耗費三年多心血建造的基地轉瞬間…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們把這裡的情報洩漏出去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才沒這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你們的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們把同伴害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  他們什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…同伴們…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛還說說笑笑的傢伙們…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解  會報仇雪恨的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…是誰向A-LAWS泄的密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的間諜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是  我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我事情的原委  沙慈·克洛斯羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙  這就是他們的做法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生於戰火  又魂歸戰火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這就是所謂的命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這就是所謂的命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不得不戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生於戰火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是友軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又魂歸戰火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這就是所謂的命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不得不戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上望不到盡頭的征程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路的盡頭…就是生命的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是神的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米里奧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米里奧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都…做了什麼蠢事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒料到會有這種結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想逃離戰爭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生這種事…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪走他們生命的就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你愚蠢的舉動造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己當作局外人  與自己無關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視之為不同的世界的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種逃避現實的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不自覺地變成惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終招致這樣的後果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也不想這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS做得好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而原因在於他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·克洛斯羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回阿扎提斯坦了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎提斯坦…我們的故國被…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎提斯坦被…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說失去了Gundam的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對反聯邦政府秘密基地的打擊卻取得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是大功一件啊  馬內金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  您討厭掃蕩戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是樂在其中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說在享受殺人的樂趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼激動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您以前不是也做過同樣的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那可是慘劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報出錯導致友軍自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時您應該是AEU的戰術預報員…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想對自己人動手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了那樣的事  理應不再介入戰爭了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可現在卻還這麼留戀？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很敬重你的哦  馬內金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎提斯坦竟然遭到了攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聯邦做的嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但參與進攻的MS中…有一架Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐似乎暈倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發出了托勒密起動命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡不知道會被如何處置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市區域的主要設施幾乎全被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是警察還是軍隊都發揮不了作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此  我還是想回到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個拉撒託付給我的國家去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧你能回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刹那強行把我帶回來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多謝他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝什麼？ 我死不足惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是為了阿扎提斯坦…我赴湯蹈火都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being似乎想把這裡缺失的器材和食物進行緊急部署
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其它設施尚未移送完成之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會參與防衛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  轉告他們解了我們的燃眉之急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是誰洩漏了這裡的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這問題問同是間諜的我好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生的Celestial Being多麼地友善啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是受誰的影響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  由我來安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給妮娜·崔尼蒂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你能用腦量子波？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要騙過改革者們  少不了她的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個任務不適合你  紅龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  兄長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和那傢伙沒有本質區別嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於精神打擊  導致一時間意識紊亂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過一會就會蘇醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚  但原因應該來自這次的殘殺事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米里奧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你的戰術預報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據錯誤的情報你們制定了各種戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後導致友軍間互相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我十分敬重一心一意關注戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為使其迅速結束而竭盡全力的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們過於優秀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬內金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…艾米里奧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九條
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam們的戰術…很像她的指揮風格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說九條她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…不  那才是真正的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校發來的密碼文？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要用頂武使用的方式？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如此轉彎抹角與你聯絡我深表歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這封信不想被A-LAWS發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說中尉你參加了卡塔隆的殲滅戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這件事  我必須向你謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝罪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為上校得到的情報  導致了這次掃蕩戰的實行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校一定十分悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候都如此在意我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我收為養女嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  這要征得你的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇摩·斯米爾諾夫這名字果然不怎麼順耳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不能再用佩麗絲這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到有一點悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜歡這個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想忘記蘊含在其中的那些往事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧上校我才重新認識到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己只是超人特務機關的一號超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是殺人的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不配擁有幸福的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失態啊  斯米爾諾夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然讓卡塔隆的參戰員逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來我特地跑來顯得…毫無意義！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然對長官出手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是政府直屬的獨立治安維持部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要把我們與聯邦軍的軍銜相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的責任全在我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上級的處分下達之前  請你繼續執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對阿扎提斯坦的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦著手中東重編
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  這可真是慘不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  工作工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==================================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴拉克·基甯上尉等補充人員五名  前來報到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡蒂·馬內金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉  你為何會加入A-LAWS？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告  在下是想為世界統一盡一份力主動申請的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有後悔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐情況怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概還需要靜養一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆方的情況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看屏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆的轉移按照預定於1200開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS會來  毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Gundam迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是戰術怎麼辦  皇小姐倒下後現在這狀況…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此我們也只能上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密向海岸線移動  得讓敵人發現我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特利麥奧斯  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,針對獨立治安維持部隊對反政府勢力的鎮壓作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全球各地爆發了報復性恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的行為  竟然演變這種地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎麼做才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除光學迷彩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦被監視衛星捕捉到的時間推定為0037
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員  做好一級戰鬥準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超兵  任何任務都要忠實地執行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為此而被創造出來的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾到您了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是作為補充人員到任的路易絲·哈萊維準尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是MS部隊所屬的蘇摩·佩麗絲中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  中尉大人  我隨隨便便就跟您說話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腦量子波是這樣感覺到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的內心在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在思念著某人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉  您在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到作戰會議的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是路易絲·哈萊維準尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉  你該回禮才是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是安德烈·斯密爾諾夫少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是少女啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視衛星捕捉到了Celestial Being的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS隊按照E3戰術計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台肩上有兩個驅動裝置的Gundam由我去迎戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要任何干涉和輔助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何不可呢  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久聞Mr.武士道大名  就讓我們見識一下你的手段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會回應你的期待  先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現我們的敵人差不多該來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓Gundam先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一  第二甲板艙門開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee  Arios  準備發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電磁彈射器電壓上升
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射出時機移交給Seravee
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  Seravee  特瑞亞·埃德  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有腦量子波…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制權移交
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認控制權
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios  阿里路亞·哈普提茲姆  出發迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  Cherudim和OO準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅  今天要認真打了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電磁系統準備完成  發射時機移交
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim  洛克恩·斯托拉托斯  進行狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  可別用TRANS-AM啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  現在還是想眼前的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO  刹那·F·清榮  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要保護卡塔隆的各位吧  請讓我也做點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的好意就心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認到A-LAWS的MS編隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將進入戰鬥空域了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得做點什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到四架Gundam  現在分成小隊進行各個擊破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙爐驅動的Gundam就交給你了  Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本小隊的目標是長翅膀的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於等到這個時侯了  媽媽  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目視確認到Gundam了  全機開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中  命中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了  要認真打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗體E-57！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪麗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈萊維準尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動攻擊打不到敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  要是里希提在的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（里希提：里希特達爾，原托勒密舵手，與克里斯蒂娜一同陣亡）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到次艦橋去負責炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就集中精力操作艦體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓監視衛星捕捉到艦體然後憑力量強攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩台MS嚴重損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將戰術轉移到C計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是九條嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  請看武士道機！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一架機體向OO突進！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度非常快！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架新型機！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊也有長進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就對了  少年！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小隊長  哈萊維準尉前往敵人母艦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下去支援她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩先生  請讓我也幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有覺悟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要保護那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  跟著來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太嫩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是A-LAWS  難纏的機師可真多！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道操作方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩架敵機正向本艦靠近！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火  他們攻過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在做什麼  開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了人的話  我就跟你們一樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了！  趕快！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥的話  又會傷害到無辜的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的行為應當被人怨恨  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子也是你們的犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…！
